  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Hedging Relationships per Derivative</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio860ada531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\"> Hedging Relationships per Derivative </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> This report shows the derivatives and the exposures they are hedging. It is thus possible to report on the derivatives that are hedging/are not hedging exposures, and where hedge capacities remain.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hedge Accounting for Exposures</span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> → </span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Information System</span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> → </span><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Hedging Relationships per Derivative</span> .\n</p></li></ul>\n<p class=\"p\"> The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hedging Relationships per Derivative</span> screen appears.\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter your selection criteria in the following entry fields:\n</p></li></ul>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Company code\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Product type\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Financial transaction\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Key date\n</p><p class=\"p\"> If you flag the field display derivative w/o hedge, derivatives that are not designated to any hedging relationship are also displayed.\n</p><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Program</span> → <span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Execute.</span>\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}